dmca.title: NoPosting of MyPictures on MySpace
dmca.body: I am the Intellectual Property (IP) owner of two websites on the Internet, which are [private] and Interstate275Florida.com.  It has been brought to my attention by way of the site server logs for Interstate275Florida.com that the aforementioned MySpace user downloaded an image from the Interstate275Florida.com website and used it as a background image on this user
